1 & 0 \\
0 & 1
\end{matrix}$$`

1 & 0 \\

\end{bmatrix}$$`

1 & 0 \\

\end{Bmatrix}$$`

等号对齐

`$$\begin{align}
f(x) 
&= (x + 1)^{2} \\
&= x^{2} + 2x + 1
\end{align}$$`

$$\begin{align} f(x) &= (x + 1)^{2} \\ &= x^{2} + 2x + 1 \end{align}$$

方程组

`$$f(x) = \begin{cases}
0, x > 0, \\
1, x \leq 0
\end{cases}$$`

$$f(x) = \begin{cases} 0, x > 0, \\ 1, x \leq 0 \end{cases}$$

`$$\begin{cases}
x + 1 = 0 \\
x + 2 = 1
\end{cases}$$`

$$\begin{cases} x + 1 = 0 \\ x + 2 = 1 \end{cases}$$
